  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n1. User drags any draggable content on the page  \n2. The portal is activated and adopts its predecessor, which destroys the originating |aura::Window|  \n3. When the user finishes or cancels the drag, |content::WebContentsViewAura::StartDragging| uses the destroyed |aura:"
